OL,3,C'Selfless' woman born with hole in
OL,4,Cheart 'brings joy' to poorly children
OL,6,FJulia Barthram went to meet the former
OL,7,Fheart patient dedicated to 'bringing
OL,8,Fjoy' to children in hospital
OL,10,FA Newcastle woman who was treated for
OL,11,Fa hole in her heart as a teenager at a
OL,12,FNewcastle hospital now runs a toy
OL,13,Fappeal for the sick children there.
OL,15,FA regular check up when Calli Tully
OL,16,Fwas 17 showed her life was in danger
OL,17,Fand she had to undergo nine hours of
OL,18,Fopen heart surgery at the Freeman
OL,19,FHospital to save her life.
