OL,3,C'Selfless' woman born with hole in
OL,4,Cheart 'brings joy' to poorly children
OL,6,FAfter she came home, all she could
OL,7,Fthink about were the children still in
OL,8,Fhospital at Christmas, so she decided
OL,9,Fto bring Christmas to them and began
OL,10,Ffundraising to buy gifts.
OL,12,FNow aged 27, she has not stopped.
OL,14,FCalli is one of four finalists for the
OL,15,FTyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year - the
OL,16,Fwinner of which will go to London to
OL,17,Fthe Pride of Britain award ceremony.
OL,19,FAfter finding out she needed surgery
OL,20,FCalli said she "didn't want to be here
OL,21,Fanymore".
