OL,3,C'Selfless' woman born with hole in
OL,4,Cheart 'brings joy' to poorly children
OL,6,FShe added: "I got a phone call from
OL,7,Fthe Freeman Hospital saying I needed
OL,8,Fto come in for immediate heart surgery.
OL,10,F"I actually hung up the phone first
OL,11,Fbecause I was so scared and then my
OL,12,FMum came home from work and said, 'we
OL,13,Fneed to go to hospital'.
OL,15,F"So we literally came straight here.
OL,16,FIt was the worst time ever, I
OL,17,Fliterally didn't want to be here any
OL,18,Fmore."
