OL,3,C'Selfless' woman born with hole in
OL,4,Cheart 'brings joy' to poorly children
OL,6,FAlthough she had been discharged and
OL,7,Freturned home, she wanted to bring joy
OL,8,Fto the children that were still
OL,9,Fundergoing treatment, so she started
OL,10,F'Calli's Heart Campaign'.
OL,12,FVicki Woof, play nurse at the Freeman
OL,13,FHospital, said: "To be able to be
OL,14,Fbrave enough to step back into an
OL,15,Fenvironment where you went through a
OL,16,Ftrauma is massive in itself.
OL,18,F"To think, actually, I want to make a
OL,19,Fdifference and I want to impact these
OL,20,Ffamilies lives, and she absolutely
OL,21,Fdoes."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
