OL,6,FMs Woof said: "When the children
OL,7,Fneeded outdoor play equipment, Calli
OL,8,Fwas there.
OL,10,F"We kind of asked and within a week we
OL,11,Fwere at the fire exit collecting it
OL,12,Fall.
OL,14,F"What Calli does brings absolute joy."
OL,16,FCalli said being nominated for a Pride
OL,17,Fof Britain Fundraiser of the Year
OL,18,F"felt absolutely amazing".
OL,20,FShe added: "It would feel so good to
OL,21,Fgo to the Pride of Britain Awards".
